The paper discusses optimization algorithms commonly used in machine learning, which falls under the category of "cs.LG" (Machine Learning). The paper also touches on neural networks and their optimization, which could fall under "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of optimization algorithms in computer vision ("cs.CV"), artificial intelligence ("cs.AI"), and distributed systems ("cs.DS").
